Structure:

1 hour per day
Daily entry Health log
10 days per lesson
36 lessons
Each lesson: podcast episode, experiment templates, discussions, resources

Experience: Assigned a learning partner, placed in a group, connected on slack with your group and community at large [$1,250 CAD]

*Validation: 1/2 page PDF per lesson, 10min video per block, final 21 min video [you, lessons, insights, your offering])


